<u>Wording of the Job Statement</u>

When describing past jobs, be sure to focus on three things:
<ul>
 	<li>Transferrable skills you learned</li>
 	<li>Accomplishments</li>
 	<li>Results or impact of what you did</li>
</ul>
This should be done using “one-line” statements that are not complete sentences, but focus on your skills by using <strong>powerful action verbs.</strong>

&nbsp;

<img class="alignnone wp-image-44247" src="http://p2i.pyd.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/Action-Verbs-resumes-2b-1000x475.png" alt="action-verbs-resumes-2b" width="750" height="356" />

<img class="alignnone wp-image-44248" src="http://p2i.pyd.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/Thesaurus-Definition-resumes-2b-1000x440.png" alt="thesaurus-definition-resumes-2b" width="750" height="330" />

<strong><u>DO NOT use words in your resume that you could not correctly use in a sentence</u></strong>

It does not look good to an employer if you use a word incorrectly!

&nbsp;

<strong><u>Formatting the Resume</u></strong>

The most important thing to remember is that the resume should be easy to read! What does this look like?
<ul>
 	<li>All headings, dates, and information should line up</li>
 	<li>Make headings and titles <strong>BOLD </strong>so they stand out</li>
 	<li>Keep all information concise</li>
</ul>
<img class="alignnone wp-image-44252" src="http://p2i.pyd.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/Concise-Definition-resumes-2b-1000x172.png" alt="concise-definition-resumes-2b" width="750" height="129" />

For example, if you worked as a camp counselor:

<strong><u>Not concise:</u></strong> “Responsible for watching and supervising a large group of students during day-to-day activities while they attended camp, including nightly cabin checks, dinner duty, and general supervision.”

<strong><u>Concise:</u></strong> “Supervised forty campers to make sure activities were safe and organized.”

&nbsp;

When writing a resume, it is not necessary to use complete sentences!

&nbsp;

&nbsp;

<img class="alignnone wp-image-44255" src="http://p2i.pyd.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/Lesson-Vocabulary-resumes-2b-904x1000.png" alt="lesson-vocabulary-resumes-2b" width="750" height="830" />

